author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Tile floor removal tips…I have to remove mosaic tiles set on top of concrete. For work like this I wear the Ironclad Command Impact glove because the padding absorbs vibration and the knuckles have rubber pads. I highly recommend these gloves if you use your hands to make a living. Many thanks to Ironclad for sponsoring this video 🔥#demo #tilefloor #homerenovation #bathroomremodel #homerepairtutor #brandpartner
